title: Interpol - KCRW Presents: Interpol Live from Los Angeles (8/26/1
description:
Interpol's concert as streamed live on NPR's website. This was a special show done in Los Angeles on August 26th, 2014. The show can be streamed here: http://www.npr.org/event/music/340189598/kcrw-presents-interpol but it's much better to be able to download it.


Setlist: Say Hello to the Angels, Evil, C'mere, Hands Away, Breaker 1 (live debut), Length of Love, My Desire, Not Even Jail, Anywhere, Same Town New Story (live debut), Take You on a Cruise, All the Rage Back Home

And a review of the show: http://www.laweekly.com/westcoastsound/2014/08/27/interpol-mark-sennett-studios-august-26-2014
